# Project Overview

This project is a V4L2 driver for the RS300 camera module. It is designed to work with the Raspberry Pi 4b running the raspberry pi OS bookworm.

# Project Structure

The project is structured as follows:

- `rs300-v4l2-driver/`: The main project directory.
- `rs300-v4l2-driver/rs300.c`: The main driver file.
- `rs300-v4l2-driver/rs300-overlay.c`: The overlay file for the driver. This is the device tree overlay for the camera.


